{"body": "@NoKarma but if the object don't respond to :some_method when you try @person.try(:some_method) || @person will raise NoMethodError.\r\n\r\nWith the proposed fetch method, if the object don't respond to :some_method it will return the last argument if present or nil. @person.fetch(:some_method, @person)\r\n\r\nThis is a shortcut to: @person.respond_to?(:some_method) ? @person.some_method : @person", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1214465", "created_at": "2011-05-21T13:59:07Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1176#issuecomment-1214465", "updated_at": "2011-05-21T13:59:07Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1176, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/ricardohsd", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/56d84b6bf4f2fed7069ad9ee24dea891?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F70607e3a9b9376b3b41ecfc024f2c89c.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/received_events", "gravatar_id": "56d84b6bf4f2fed7069ad9ee24dea891", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "ricardohsd", "type": "User", "id": 46654, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ricardohsd/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52385c31bd3543c151011ecc"}, "id": 1214465, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1176"}
